ews.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=370075&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370075%26refer%3DShare&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=9ae5ea46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D370075%26refer%3DShare&h=0f03846d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=370075&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"b3353943cc605eb857211e103201bd2a8bb20d09","tid":1724211,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec1897331725abc169a5ece4a5097a1341f72f21","tid":1724211,"uid":87511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"留意返，呢間係私院，唔係公院<br />\n<br />\n呢間醫院都係鬼鬼地，塞你兩三日，就話自己求診個案減少咗<br />\n即係點？唔塞你就會多咗人病？你生意就會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日先有個自稱係醫院staff嘅人想埋嚟講數，又係講差唔多嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n第一，popo前幾晚射催淚彈，你有冇貼啲紙喺醫院叫警察高抬貴手？浸中附近都有好多國際學校啊<br />\n第二，如果想浸中讓埋金城道行車線，要睇浸中有冇人肯搞個閘出嚟放車出入，但係要人長期站哨"},{"pid":"66e9ceb259d2a5f88a027f57c004ff4e4ee4aa94","tid":1724211,"uid":45979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"#手足投稿<br />\n<br />\n1）窩打老道仲有車路，<br />\n救護車/的士/私家車可以到達<br />\n2）運血車一定都可以上去<br />\n3）職員唔一定係廣播道返工，<br />\n我仲起FB 見前同事行到去返工（經九龍塘方向入）<br />\n4）我星期三返過黎， 見過有醫生（我認得）、病人（拎住藥袋）步行去九龍塘方向離開<br />\n<br />\n手足唔好俾呢d搧情文擾亂到"},{"pid":"e1792459ef1bfbb2307d584a8fb4c506ece60051","tid":1724211,"uid":45979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsUjvZa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsUjvZa.jpg&h=068fb87d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"479190cc6412b7ae7e452fa9d88afd3e43e6e194","tid":1724211,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:08:48.000Z","msg":